flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("[24F282B6434E981D3FBC5B9E3C7849C5]", "FDDF3F7E44FACA21B8A93CBF3716EB11", "In a matter of heartbeats, I\'ve left Sanctus and the world I knew behind for the promised wonders of Verra. I can sense the power of essence all around me.The Restoration\'s Hammer takes their mission to restore the ancient Dunzenkell Mountainhall as the seat of Dunir power in Verra. They\'ve established Hammer Rest to the East, but have had unexpected trouble.Gatewatcher Borin Stonebeard has tasked me with reaching Gritstone Overwatch, a forward post on the Old King\'s Road on the way to Hammer Rest. The commander there, Gretta Ironhand, is facing a growing threat from mysterious and hostile Clay Dwarves whose origins are unknown. I must report to her.")
mainObjectiveText: NSLOCTEXT("[24F282B6434E981D3FBC5B9E3C7849C5]", "0775292C42E7E57B61195BA6B4F66486", "Make your way to Gritstone Overwatch and if possible, help along the way.")
name: ANV_FTUE_HR_0001_TheBrokenLine
